{"tid":202300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與世隔絕幾十年, 成功脫北者第一次見到今日的科技","createTime":"2017-04-15T11:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T07:12:16.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b10279a30d1701b41155480a08faec2e93ed8e4","tid":202300,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">與世隔絕幾十年, 成功脫北者第一次見到今日的科技<br />\n<a href=\"https://c6up.com/2017/04/13/%E8%88%87%E4%B8%96%E9%9A%94%E7%B5%95%E5%B9%BE%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4-%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%84%AB%E5%8C%97%E8%80%85%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc6up.com%2F2017%2F04%2F13%2F%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%2596%25E9%259A%2594%25E7%25B5%2595%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2584%25AB%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%2F&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=d72cfeab\" target=\"_blank\">https://c6up.com/2017/04/13/%E8%88%87%E4%B8%96%E9%9A%94%E7%B5%95%E5%B9%BE%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4-%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%84%AB%E5%8C%97%E8%80%85%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80/</a></div></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.price.com.hk/space/news/images/20170413/91a88a659dff7be92755.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fspace%2Fnews%2Fimages%2F20170413%2F91a88a659dff7be92755.jpg&h=ab107276&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n早前有脫北者來港演說，雖然對於講者的演說內容坊間甚有質疑，但是無可否認，脫北者需要重新適應這個對他們而言的陌生社會。簡單如銀行的基本概念、信用咭的使用方法、自動櫃員機&hellip;對於他們而言卻是全新的概念。近日《華爾街日報》推出一段短片，訪問了幾位脫北者和他們的日常生活所遇到的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://m.wsj.net/video/20170328/032817_nkdefect4/032817_nkdefect4_v2_ec664k.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.wsj.net%2Fvideo%2F20170328%2F032817_nkdefect4%2F032817_nkdefect4_v2_ec664k.mp4&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=5001e390\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.wsj.net/video/20170328/032817_nkdefect4/032817_nkdefect4_v2_ec664k.mp4</a></div><br />\n<br />\n「以前在北韓未有見過 ATM，所以真的以為機器內入面有人」。可能對於大家而言機械化與日常生活密不可分，但對脫北者而言卻是活生生的文化衝擊。為協助脫北者，南韓政府及志願機構亦舉辦各種課程及活動，讓他們能融入社會。"},{"pid":"9f13097a66c7c0c51e6f775297ec2c598cf3a22e","tid":202300,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:58:05.000Z","msg":"Atm真係有人"},{"pid":"04d033d0d8aeac853fe19b3c6a08ce0ab643644f","tid":202300,"uid":89743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:03:10.000Z","msg":"原來好多會員都喺脫北者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c695a4a972bd7f7f86de3a79c0248df34a0db09","tid":202300,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:03:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rk3rX-9qLrY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRk3rX-9qLrY&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=8d11cb56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rk3rX-9qLrY</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WAHfYZYvEx4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWAHfYZYvEx4&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a36a29d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WAHfYZYvEx4</a>"},{"pid":"5128ad03dd9387f9dd18093127b79e8cbb33e04b","tid":202300,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來好多會員都喺脫北者<img src=